name: Cafe Cotinga

reviews.review_text: Good place to eat. Reasonably priced. Went there for lunch as a party of 4 with 2 kids. The food was good. Probably also ordered a bit too much. Service was good. Some pictures of the food have been shown. Their hummus and mayo, which we ordered, seemed to all be freshly made and taste very good. Could not fault the food. Would definitely go again.

Cafe Cotinga is part of the small Tamarind hotel. Well located right on the main road, its a charming cafe,restaurant  with full Bar facilities.
The service, food quality is always good and the ambience is lovely too. They have plenty of open air sitting in the verandah and garden as well as an indoor air-conditioned seating area.
The menu covers breakfast  Lunch, Dinner, snack choices as well as juices, spirits and cocktails. They have a fabulous pastry counter too.
There's a pool table too. Live bands play there on some days.

Love the concept of LATE COFFEE. Because after a good dinner, I am a dessert and coffee person! And at the Cafe Continga they have the best cakes available even if you arrive at 23:30 after your dinner time. I visit this place 5 years ago when I used to live in Anjuna, and yesterday I return for a dark chocolate cake and cappuccino. LOVE the place. Definitely coming back for more.

description:
Nestled in the vibrant landscape of Anjuna, **Cafe Cotinga** boasts an impressive rating of **4.5** based on the feedback from **4,124 patrons**. This charming eatery has won the hearts of many, particularly for its delightful **English breakfast**, decadent **cheesecakes**, flaky **croissants**, and scrumptious **banoffee pie**—treats that frequently grace the tables of satisfied customers.

### Ambiance & Design

The ambiance at Cafe Cotinga reflects a sunny disposition, perfectly suited for both casual gatherings and special occasions. Reviews describe it as part of the inviting **Tamarind Hotel**, located conveniently on the main road. Guests can choose from abundant **open-air seating** set in a verdant garden or comfortable **indoor air-conditioned areas**. The decor blends rustic charm with airy simplicity, enhancing the overall dining experience. Diners have enjoyed the leisurely atmosphere accented by the gentle sounds of live bands. A recent photograph highlights the cafe’s cozy outdoor setup, complete with lush greenery, inviting guests to unwind over their meals ([image](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdks8_bT5R3OpBrHtCpc8CFy4ojEZyQ64hU_h8J1ErlQL0ql9tHUWoz09ArLF9a5DwlW3FlsrQQR6uGpqnxZC4Lsax4IKHlLqOmi5gVFIBqRpPi0nM0j1q15Oq6iopCAYPPAcIf2=w375-h281-p)).

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The culinary offerings are a testament to the cafe’s dedication to quality and variety. Their **menu** covers breakfast, lunch, and dinner, complemented by an array of exciting snack options and a tempting pastry counter boasting an impressive selection. Standout dishes celebrated by guests include freshly-made hummus, rich dark chocolate cake, and indulgent cheesecakes. As detailed in the reviews, the presentation is impeccable, with dishes crafted not only to satisfy the taste buds but to please the eyes as well. The **persistence in serving quality**, as noted in a patron's recollection of their past experiences, indicates that the cafe has remained a favorite through the years.

### Customer Experience & Service

Cafe Cotinga excels in creating a welcoming atmosphere for families and individuals alike. Reviewers consistently express satisfaction with the **friendly and attentive service**, describing staff members as efficient and keen to ensure delightful dining experiences. One family recounts a pleasant lunch outing, enjoying a variety of dishes with their children, asserting they would "definitely go again." This family-friendly environment is enriched by the cafe’s **reservation and walk-in readiness**, allowing for seamless dining without the fuss.

### Popularity & Reviews

The social media buzz surrounding Cafe Cotinga reflects a lively community of diners enthusiastic about sharing their experiences. Each interaction tells a story of returning customers and fresh visitors alike. Critics have applauded the establishment for its pleasant surroundings, diverse menu, and consistently high food quality. Celebrated for its late-night offerings, the cafe has garnered a reputation for being a go-to spot for dessert seekers and coffee enthusiasts, with glowing reviews about its delectable cakes.

### Utilizing Visual Content

The visual storytelling of Cafe Cotinga shines through customer-shared photos that capture the inviting ambiance and beautifully plated dishes. Images of stellar desserts, such as the **cheesecake** and **banoffee pie**, reveal an artistic flair in their preparation, inviting dessert lovers to indulge ([image](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlzWwCu6y43PmOO0IAzWd2X57V4av0CBeIQuIlADtC_96C6Pd3_AyTv8KQRn2ya0POKn0bYIDrE7hZohqWyao1nFN2j1C79Vb4yYX5klhhe_3ukpjcJ_CFRQwkupHVgAc1WrAiW=w375-h281-p)).

### Conclusion

In summary, **Cafe Cotinga** stands as a culinary gem in Anjuna, where the blend of charm, quality, and friendliness creates an unforgettable dining experience. For those seeking a delightful escape into a world of delicious English breakfast options and sweet desserts, this cafe has earned its place as a beloved destination appealing to both locals and travelers alike. Each visit promises not just a meal, but a celebration of flavors and memories waiting to be made.
